      • setBoundsBias

        public PlaceAutocomplete.IntentBuilder setBoundsBias(LatLngBounds latLngBounds)
        Set the bounds that the Place Picker map should be centered on. If not set, you should request android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION in your manifest so that the map will be centered on the user's current location. If this permission is not present results will not be limited by any bounds.
